<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 02:05:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>心灵可能比大脑更古老迈克尔·莱文谈生命与智力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/mind-may-be-older-than-the-brain-michael-levin-on-life-and-intelligence</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 02:05:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/mind-may-be-older-than-the-brain-michael-levin-on-life-and-intelligence</guid></item><item><title>Next-潜在预测变压器学习紧凑世界模型</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/next-latent-prediction-transformers-learn-compact-world-models</link><description>查看最近的讨论。摘要：Transformer 用随着序列长度和自我关注而增长的记忆取代了循环，从而能够对过去的标记进行临时查找。因此，他们缺乏将历史压缩为具有一致转换规则的紧凑潜在状态的内在动机。这通常会导致学习解决方案泛化能力较差。我们引入了下一个潜在预测（NextLat），它通过潜在空间中的自我监督预测来扩展标准的下一个令牌训练。具体来说，NextLat 训练变压器来学习潜在表示，这些表示可以预测给定下一个标记的下一个潜在状态。从理论上讲，我们证明这些潜在因素可证明向信念状态收敛，压缩了预测未来所需的历史信息。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/next-latent-prediction-transformers-learn-compact-world-models2.png" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 01:50:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/next-latent-prediction-transformers-learn-compact-world-models</guid></item><item><title>一种常见的维生素可以帮助对抗最致命的脑癌之一</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/a-common-vitamin-could-help-fight-one-of-the-deadliest-brain-cancers</link><description>一项临床试验正在探索高剂量的维生素 B3 是否可以为胶质母细胞瘤患者提供更好的机会抵抗侵袭性脑癌。科学家发现烟酸可能有助于恢复肿瘤关闭的免疫细胞，使它们能够更有效地攻击癌症。早期结果令人鼓舞，患者的无进展生存期明显好于预期。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-common-vitamin-could-help-fight-one-of-the-deadliest-brain-cancers.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 01:35:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/a-common-vitamin-could-help-fight-one-of-the-deadliest-brain-cancers</guid></item><item><title>拉尔夫·默克尔谈倒置模式扫描隧道显微镜</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/ralph-merkle-on-inverted-mode-scanning-tunneling-microscopy</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 01:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/ralph-merkle-on-inverted-mode-scanning-tunneling-microscopy</guid></item><item><title>为什么时间旅行在中国被禁止</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/why-time-travel-is-banned-in-china</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 01:05:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/why-time-travel-is-banned-in-china</guid></item><item><title>固态材料将可见光转化为太阳光强度下的高能紫外线，扩大太阳能潜力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/solid-state-material-turns-visible-light-into-high-energy-uv-at-sunlight-intensity-expanding-solar-energy-potential</link><description>两杯温水并不能变成一杯开水。但在量子世界中，多个低能光子可以结合产生一个更高能量的光子。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/solid-state-material-turns-visible-light-into-high-energy-uv-at-sunlight-intensity-expanding-solar-energy-potential.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 00:50:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/solid-state-material-turns-visible-light-into-high-energy-uv-at-sunlight-intensity-expanding-solar-energy-potential</guid></item><item><title>科学家重新编程大脑免疫细胞来对抗阿尔茨海默病：研究</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/scientists-reprogram-brain-immune-cells-to-fight-alzheimers-study</link><description>一项突破性的研究表明，新发现的分子 OLE 可以恢复阿尔茨海默病中大脑免疫细胞的保护功能，减少有毒斑块的积累并增强记忆力。这项研究可能为对抗阿尔茨海默病的新治疗方法铺平道路。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-reprogram-brain-immune-cells-to-fight-alzheimers-study.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 00:35:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/scientists-reprogram-brain-immune-cells-to-fight-alzheimers-study</guid></item><item><title>科学家打开了隐藏在新西兰地下的一百万年前的时间胶囊</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/scientists-open-a-million-year-old-time-capsule-hidden-beneath-new-zealand</link><description>新西兰的一个洞穴出土了大约一百万年前消失的生态系统的化石，其中包括可能是鸮鹦鹉的飞行祖先。这一发现表明，早在人类到来之前，火山和气候剧变就正在重塑该国的野生动物并导致物种灭绝。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-open-a-million-year-old-time-capsule-hidden-beneath-new-zealand.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 00:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/scientists-open-a-million-year-old-time-capsule-hidden-beneath-new-zealand</guid></item><item><title>詹姆斯·休斯谈《公民机器人：审问并参与世界》</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/james-hughes-on-citizen-cyborg-interrogate-and-engage-the-world</link><description>&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/james-hughes-on-citizen-cyborg-interrogate-and-engage-the-world.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 00:05:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/james-hughes-on-citizen-cyborg-interrogate-and-engage-the-world</guid></item><item><title>电池“沐浴”可将废锂离子电池恢复至 95% 电量，回收成本降低 56%</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/battery-bath-restores-spent-lithium-ion-cells-to-95-power-cuts-recycling-costs-56</link><description>为锂离子电池提供动力的关键矿物需求量很大但供应短缺，特别是对于美国来说，它必须依赖镍和钴等进口资源来制造该技术。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/battery-bath-restores-spent-lithium-ion-cells-to-95-power-cuts-recycling-costs-56.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 23:50:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/battery-bath-restores-spent-lithium-ion-cells-to-95-power-cuts-recycling-costs-56</guid></item></channel></rss>